Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ProSeka AfterTalk, "This Story Carries Hope" Edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that okay just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit your hand, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty solid hit, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mayu Yoshioka, who plays Haruka Kiritani from MORE MORE JUMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this ProSeka AfterTalk is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a program where we look back at the event while introducing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the messages we received from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it's the "This Story Carries Hope" edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,did you enjoy the story and the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I myself was really looking forward to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm really looking forward to hearing everyone's thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,today, including this broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we were previously collecting messages
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for AfterTalk via the official ProSeka Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and email.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to everyone who sent them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we'll be introducing the messages we received during the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we really received a lot of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, your thoughts on the event and this broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,please post them using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I can see the YouTube chat here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, keep on writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be checking the hashtag after the broadcast ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so please tweet a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so, while I'll be looking at the comments,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep things moving along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I came here today planning to talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my notebook today, but I forgot it in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask the makeup artist to get it for me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,let's immediately talk about the story of this event, 'Carrying Hope'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everyone, what did you think of this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While introducing your letters, we'll look back at the story together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,First up, from Mirin-san, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From: Mirin-san. Yoshioka-san, Kon-more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kon-more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Yoshioka-san's strong, clear voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that this event's story depicted the process of reaching an answer more subtly than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A note arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce it shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a bit slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone discussed and exchanged opinions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way they thought, debating 'this way or that way,' was clearly depicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan, who moved efficiently among them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan's initiative became even clearer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was fun to see her interacting with various idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to everyone in Momojan in the LumiGra finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's abbreviated as LumiGra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lumina Grand Prix is the common name, but this is the first time I've seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,abbreviated with four characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Has that happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirin-san, thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It was a very significant milestone story, being the one right before the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's reactions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the feeling was, 'Are they finally coming?' I got that from the messages I received beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were many such impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I heard there were many people who were really bracing themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, it felt like they were in a really
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,good state to move on to the next stage, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a boss like Haruka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw "Rumigura," I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, so that's what it is." It seems like it's being abbreviated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it feels like it's going to become a common nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world. It's likely to be abbreviated as "Rumigura."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense, makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so with that, I'd like to read another message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, is it Yukky-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukky-san, in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Yoshioka-san, konmuha desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Konmuha desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This story felt like a culmination of sorts for Momo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Working together with the girls they'd fought alongside during the Lumina Grand Prix,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they prioritized delivering hope to the people in front of them, rather than focusing on audience numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was deeply moved by that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the way Haruka and the others tackled their challenges, as if confronting their past selves,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and the different shades of Haruka that Yoshioka-san shows us through her voice, I'm looking forward to them in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They safely passed in second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment the results were announced, my heart was pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Little by little, one group at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, the total number of votes being displayed as a number, isn't that incredibly realistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Something interesting about the Lumina Grand Prix is that each person gets two votes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just one vote per person, so you can choose 'this one and this one,' for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of nice, and also, when you look at the total number of votes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look at the numbers, you realize just how much attention it received,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I really feel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that kind of format, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's such an interesting project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the real world, to decide an idol that gets the whole of Japan excited like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a participatory event like that is pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I found myself constantly substituting and wondering what it would be like if it happened in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I voted for Momo-chan and Rewrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, on the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where would I put my votes, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were also units that appeared by name, even though they weren't in the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of team they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and imagining that was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, two votes per person, but someone said you can't vote for the same place twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said it in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time 4th place was announced, it was already confirmed that someone would be pushed out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And realizing there that not all four groups could advance, I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the group called 'I'm' advanced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of unit they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that unexpected second place was a big deal, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it was predicted differently online,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan mentioned something like that at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, what rank do you think it would be,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,based on your gut feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're watching, thinking it's real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan, with the online vote counts and predictions...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They use all of that as a reference for their future productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They really take all the hints they can get,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then think about what to do next. I thought that was really mature of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're high schoolers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think high schoolers can do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you very much for all your messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yukki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we only received these two messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really want to talk a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so please let me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,take my time and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for ProSeka users, the Lumina Grand Prix
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,must have felt like it took a really,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept releasing it little by little, and you wondered when the preliminaries would finally end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this feeling of wanting to see what happens next quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but then again, I also wished it would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was right in that in-between state, at the moment it went from the preliminaries to the finals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was incredibly nervous, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more, when I realized it was Haruka's banner, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,'Wait, is this story going to be told from Haruka's perspective?'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, especially in Haruka's case, as I'll talk about a bit later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a clear wall: Hiiragi-san and Rewrite,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That existence she can't help but be aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And she has to confront them again, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, when she fought with Hiiragi-san—well, 'fought' is one way to put it—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,when they confronted each other one-on-one and talked,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it depicted something like a battle with adults in the real industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and Haruka's expression was very dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was a growth amidst thinking, 'Oh no, I might not be able to overcome this wall.'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time, again, I wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,'Wow, what kind of battle will she have with Hiiragi-san now?'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that happened, before the finals, the advice she received from Rewrite,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who had become her comrades, her team, I thought, 'Is it really this reassuring?'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you make them an ally, that reassurance, that strength, that overwhelming presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sense of security that 'if this person is here, it'll be fine,' all of that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,was conveyed from every single word of Hiiragi-san. This is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,where Haruka respects, where she wants to aim, and also
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the big thing she has to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt like there was a wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it episode 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san's presence is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the more dependable she becomes, the more I feel the threat of what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it makes me even more curious about what kind of team Aslan was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the one Haruka was in with Hiiragi-san back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Haruka, it's Hiiragi-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the bigger picture, I think other teams went to various places for events,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,starting with cram schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Arisa-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Her thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from a former idol's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,were 'I wanted to do this, but I can't now.'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wants to entrust that power to these new kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The idols in this world, their... influence?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's insane, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.56,0:22:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt throughout the story that you guys, being entrusted by these legendary idols,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, Kiriya's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely love that line where she says 'I was struck'.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was recording, I, of course, only received the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't able to record together, so the finished product...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear for the first time when I play the game. But the scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...was already so good, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that scene with Arisa-san and Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That one was just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of played just to see that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I wanted to see all of Momo-chan's scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I especially wanted to engrave that one into my memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made sure to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems there's an adjustment happening, so the screen will go dark for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make some adjustments, so please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:23:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep talking, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll wait for the next comment to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can everyone hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can you hear me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed that everyone's comments
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,have returned, so let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.63,0:24:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.15,0:24:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um, there are 8 episodes in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been talking about Episode 6 this whole time, but let's talk about the other episodes too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The traveling Team Live lasted two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.32,0:24:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realize again that the previous Lumina Grand Prix events were held over much shorter periods,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought what they were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.43,0:25:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even before, they'd switch with other teams and shuffle songs to perform, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to think they were doing that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,every few days... everyone's memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.28,0:25:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're so young, that was my honest impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of speed is just amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for active idols to learn songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.32,0:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was talk about Minori being good at free copying,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but even members who aren't like that still have to learn other units' songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.47,0:25:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,learn the songs, learn the dances, think about formations,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and perform them originally, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.36,0:25:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have to bring out their own strengths too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much to think about, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.95,0:25:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They do it so well, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to learn from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.28,0:25:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.95,0:25:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, the thing I found most interesting and couldn't stop watching was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.36,0:25:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:26:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time, the comments from viewers...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.88,0:26:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...that appear in Momojan's event stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think everyone writes them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen them before, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I feel like there's a dedicated writer for those comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.56,0:26:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so spot-on every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.47,0:26:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet there are a lot of people who think, "Oh, I feel like I've tweeted something like this before."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.41,0:26:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.91,0:26:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.47,0:26:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, so either they're pulling comments from somewhere, or they're hiring someone specifically for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.91,0:26:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so real every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really interesting, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like that's one of the things that makes it feel so real, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time, I'm a little curious, you know, in this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.47,0:27:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...what's the comment that I thought, "Oh, I'd probably say that myself," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.67,0:27:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, sometimes they're lines of dialogue, but there are also depictions of fans, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.15,0:27:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like Momojan's fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.43,0:27:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, oh, right, it's a blessing that we don't hear that much anymore, compared to how it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.63,0:27:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped appearing, but back then, when people would say, "I don't know Momojan," you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.56,0:27:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.95,0:27:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The other members were already doing their thing, but back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.32,0:27:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there were some really harsh comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.88,0:27:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.23,0:27:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it that way, the current environment is really great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.95,0:27:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me so happy that everyone says, 'Yeah, Momojan!'
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.32,0:28:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.84,0:28:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten a lot kinder, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.43,0:28:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just that it's gotten kinder, but it means Momojan has
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,become known to everyone, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like appearing on TV and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.15,0:28:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think the power of comments is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.39,0:28:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to their efforts, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.15,0:28:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Momojan's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.56,0:28:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.76,0:28:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone can look at the comments and feel welcome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.71,0:28:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can watch them with peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.84,0:28:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.99,0:28:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If Momojan were to do a stream by themselves, the chat section
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.63,0:28:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,would probably change quite a bit, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.91,0:28:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The vibe, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.47,0:29:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but there are probably fans who've been supporting them since back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.63,0:29:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so that might not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.91,0:29:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're new, saying they just came
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.43,0:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from watching the Lumina Grand Prix.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.95,0:29:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's nice. You know, originally...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.76,0:29:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, first-timers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.95,0:29:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that happens, that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.19,0:29:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, 'Hello, first-timers!'
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.71,0:29:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd actually blurt it out in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.56,0:29:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Like, 'I came from Lumigra.'
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.15,0:29:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what if 'Lumigra' gets officially adopted? What would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.15,0:29:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.88,0:29:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just the one saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.41,0:29:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.91,0:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I've already done a general recap, so now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.63,0:30:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's put Episode 8 aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.23,0:30:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you a scene I personally want to talk about. As you might guess, it's from Episode 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.76,0:30:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.80,0:30:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.63,0:30:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually considered Episode 8, but if I watch that, I'll just cry my eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.15,0:30:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The current ranking prediction for Rewrite is Hiiragi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.95,0:30:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth place, or fifth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.04,0:30:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right on the border of making it to the main competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.63,0:30:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.12,0:30:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.88,0:30:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that you can still get a good rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.56,0:30:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This event isn't fully taking shape yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.23,0:30:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even going all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.19,0:30:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't it great that even without going all in, you can still say you got a good rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.12,0:30:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:30:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiritani.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:30:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.63,0:31:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.47,0:31:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize I'd crossed my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.15,0:31:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I get nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,just seeing Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.91,0:31:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.95,0:31:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem like we just ran into each other by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.99,0:31:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.28,0:31:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.56,0:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I heard from Tsubaki-san and the others that Hiiragi-san would be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.67,0:31:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.52,0:31:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.12,0:31:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.28,0:31:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.52,0:31:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.15,0:31:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.12,0:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.91,0:31:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surprising, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.84,0:31:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.88,0:31:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.63,0:31:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,could you please give us some advice
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.39,0:31:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,for our event that we're holding at Lumina Time this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.99,0:31:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, wasn't it supposed to be a project you yourselves came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.12,0:32:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.39,0:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules stated that we should think of everything, including the setlist and staging.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.63,0:32:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's no problem asking for advice on the overall concept and production policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.95,0:32:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a preemptive move.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.63,0:32:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I also confirmed with the management.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I confirmed with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.04,0:32:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.32,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.36,0:32:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this Grand Prix, you're Rewrite's rivals, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.04,0:32:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.76,0:32:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking, but you already know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.76,0:32:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I believe there's no producer who has aimed to deliver hope and actually done so more than you, Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who can put it into words. Besides, we and Rewrite are on the same team right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.32,0:32:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This time's results will also affect Rewrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.12,0:32:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewrite's projected rank is currently 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.67,0:32:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't lend a hand, their chances of winning are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.19,0:32:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's from here, from this point on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.47,0:33:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that's the case, it's not 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.32,0:33:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's also a possibility of them being eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.76,0:33:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to increase our chances of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.88,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.23,0:33:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can high schoolers even use 'angle' like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.80,0:33:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.71,0:33:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.47,0:33:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, I beg of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.52,0:33:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To win,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.63,0:33:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and to deliver hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,please give us your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.76,0:33:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They specifically chose the phrase 'to deliver hope' here, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.56,0:33:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.36,0:33:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're struggling because we lack a clear criteria for how to narrow down the ideas we've come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.43,0:33:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, show me that document.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.43,0:33:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a list of the event ideas we currently have.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.19,0:33:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, so well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:33:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.88,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all the ideas themselves are good,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.88,0:34:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but how should we organize them for the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.71,0:34:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about whether you can create a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.36,0:34:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A path?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.07,0:34:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.36,0:34:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the question is whether we can create a path
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.47,0:34:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who find it difficult to move forward to believe in a story of hope again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be the criterion for judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.43,0:34:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A story of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.55,0:34:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.59,0:34:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't breathe just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.88,0:34:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.11,0:34:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san gave you advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.91,0:34:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.39,0:34:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.11,0:34:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd go talk to a producer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.99,0:34:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,from another group. I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.72,0:35:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, he's the one who can view these kinds of events most objectively, so I thought he'd surely give me good ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.59,0:35:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really see him as a person, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.24,0:35:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first asked us for Hiiragi-san's schedule, we were surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making such a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to sort things out in my head, so I wanted to talk to him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.07,0:35:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san is a reliable person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.91,0:35:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.16,0:35:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the advice I got from Hiiragi-san was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.28,0:35:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,build the entire event with our rivals and become a bit more open with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.64,0:35:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.47,0:35:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.84,0:35:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're streaming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.95,0:35:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing what happens after, I guess this could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.51,0:35:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But even for Hikari-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.80,0:35:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this wouldn't make for good streaming, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.59,0:36:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.88,0:54:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like the 3DMVs from the early days,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.11,0:54:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,where they'd just dance on stage and perform across the whole stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.84,0:54:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.20,0:54:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the recent MVs are like, actual music videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.95,0:54:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? They really feel like music videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.28,0:54:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They've evolved into 3DMVs where you can better understand the world of the song, including its lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.88,0:54:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And for this one, the lighting is also amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.16,0:54:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there was the card illustration, but this lighting from the tunnel stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.36,0:54:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the five lights shining from the background?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.95,0:54:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.07,0:54:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.16,0:54:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're consistently good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.11,0:54:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I can't stop watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.76,0:54:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.36,0:54:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.55,0:54:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should definitely check out Airi's blown kiss and...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.11,0:55:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's wink with your favorite character.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.16,0:55:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Airi's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.03,0:55:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you watch this MV, the impression it leaves is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.91,0:55:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.64,0:55:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.24,0:55:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.47,0:55:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I'm talking about the song, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.43,0:55:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, it's a song called "Polaris".
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.68,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's songs have always been cool, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.43,0:55:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, I was really looking forward to what kind of song would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.51,0:55:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned that there's a range even within "cool" from the last two songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.32,0:55:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.28,0:55:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.99,0:55:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a different kind of idol cool, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.20,0:55:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, my first impression was that it was beautiful and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.59,0:55:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The refined coolness really struck me as fresh and impactful; that was my first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And especially, there are a few past songs, but this is one of those with beautiful harmonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.84,0:56:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's one of them. Everyone sings in unison,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.28,0:56:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and then layering scales like climbing stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.68,0:56:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,how Momojan's recent story shows them gradually growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.39,0:56:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,definitely achieving success,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.47,0:56:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting results.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.16,0:56:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like that really links up with this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.59,0:56:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that kind of harmony, the whole song is just wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.39,0:56:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in terms of harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.51,0:56:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They layer so many notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.88,0:56:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are parts where each person sings individually, and parts where they're in the chorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.07,0:56:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so please listen to that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.51,0:56:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like you to compare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.80,0:56:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When we recorded this song, what I felt most strongly was,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.80,0:56:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,songs like this inevitably make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.24,0:56:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are parts where you want to sing as if you're about to cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.99,0:56:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but because we're idols, we have to deliver hope to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.07,0:56:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we absolutely can't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.51,0:56:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a song about remembering the past, feeling nostalgic,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.39,0:56:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and reaffirming that we'll work even harder now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.76,0:57:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while retaining its preciousness and coolness,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.64,0:57:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it became a song with a strong sense of nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.91,0:57:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.47,0:57:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.72,0:57:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what I wrote in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.80,0:57:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.72,0:57:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.91,0:57:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the 2DMV will be released too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.24,0:57:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it says that, the full version will probably be released too, right? That's what it means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.80,0:57:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, if you listen to the full version, I think you'll see parts
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.76,0:57:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that aren't in this short version.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.03,0:57:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely want you to compare it to the short version.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.36,0:57:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, I think the way the last chorus is sung gives a different
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.28,0:57:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,impression than previous choruses, so please listen carefully and distinguish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.51,0:57:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a personal story, but
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.43,0:57:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Mayu Yoshioka, personally wrote lyrics for a song with the North Star as its theme before,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.55,0:57:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Polaris, you know, it means something like the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.91,0:58:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idols and stars, especially the North Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.36,0:58:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,have a really high affinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.72,0:58:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was writing it back then, I thought, you know, it's a landmark or a guide for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.91,0:58:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the stars in the sky, it's like the brightest, the first star.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.59,0:58:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's used as a guiding star.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.28,0:58:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It really links to the idea of 'look at me, support me, find me'.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.28,0:58:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The North Star, that part of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.43,0:58:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This story, especially, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.47,0:58:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the image of an idol as seen through the Lumina Grand Prix,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.07,0:58:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it really links to that. I was like, 'Yeah, that's right.' And the story, you know, they were saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.91,0:58:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of idols,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.80,0:58:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're creating a story,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.03,0:58:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's absolutely necessary in a story that you create with the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This guiding principle, I really felt it,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.16,0:59:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, in these lyrics, in this poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.95,0:59:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was really emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.76,0:59:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I'm sorry this is a personal story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.88,0:59:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at this poem, looking at this title, I felt like I was really praised,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.95,0:59:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,like, 'Oh, I wasn't wrong'.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.20,0:59:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I really felt like it was good to believe in this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.99,0:59:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And my thoughts on what an idol is, what I already had,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.32,0:59:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,plus what Haruka taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.72,0:59:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized it wasn't wrong. And from now on, Momojan...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.43,0:59:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a great opportunity to reconfirm my thoughts on what an idol is,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.16,0:59:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm really glad they wrote such a wonderful song for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.95,0:59:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, up until now, the theme of 'stars' has always been associated with Leoni
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.55,1:00:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in ProSeka, and other units have avoided using it as a theme.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.24,1:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard on-site that at this point, when things have settled,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.68,1:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they wanted to challenge themselves by making 'stars' a theme.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.68,1:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at this important timing, Haruka was entrusted with this challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.55,1:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it made me genuinely happy, simply put.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.88,1:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much more I want to talk about, but the main point I want to emphasize
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.16,1:00:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is the difference in harmony and the chorus towards the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.24,1:00:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So please check out the full version and the differences with the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.16,1:00:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The 3DMV is uploaded on ProSeka's official YouTube channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.55,1:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I talked too much, it's already public.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.88,1:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.28,1:01:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So please make sure to watch that part.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.51,1:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.59,1:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.47,1:01:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and everyone, the stage decorations
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.64,1:01:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 3DMV are really great too, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.20,1:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, time flew by, but
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.84,1:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,this ProSeka AfterTalk, "This Story Carries Hope" edition,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.24,1:01:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost at its end.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.51,1:01:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll take a look at everyone's comments one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.07,1:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.91,1:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm not very articulate.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.68,1:01:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the opportunity to watch the 3DMV together with all of you was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.24,1:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all giving comments in real-time like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.99,1:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.28,1:01:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly enjoyable to share this time and connect with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.84,1:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.88,1:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for my otaku rambling.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.07,1:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there were many parts where you couldn't understand what I was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.36,1:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.43,1:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Haruka's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.88,1:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is, Haruka is cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.03,1:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably become even more
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.11,1:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,unbelievably cool from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.51,1:02:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to be like that, and I hope so too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.24,1:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As a producer, at this point,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.20,1:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they've become even more established.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.20,1:02:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, even more established.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.55,1:02:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but when I read Momojan's recent stories,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.55,1:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.07,1:02:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The excitement of what's next,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.07,1:02:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of what's going to happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.18,1:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is stronger, and I have no worries.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.68,1:02:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have any concerns.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.59,1:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's probably because everyone in Momojan has always stuck to their core principle
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.64,1:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of giving hope to their fans, without wavering,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.68,1:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept moving
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.68,1:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,towards their goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.55,1:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because they've been steadily progressing, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.55,1:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.26,1:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look back, the thrilling and heart-pounding moments
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.76,1:02:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to feel are already nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.28,1:02:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.28,1:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,now,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.06,1:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can now see it from the perspective of, 'What kind of hope
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.43,1:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,will they give us next?'
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.39,1:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly feel that's a sign of growth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.39,1:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is growth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.22,1:02:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Momojan is truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.72,1:02:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.86,1:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan is just the best, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.11,1:02:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan is the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.03,1:03:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.20,1:03:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, as you all know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.16,1:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it was announced the other day on the ProSeka Broadcast Station,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.88,1:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that this episode will be the final AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.28,1:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ending.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.24,1:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really okay for me to be the last one?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.99,1:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've been talking so much, and my inner fan came out. Was that alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.47,1:03:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.47,1:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've hinted at, being able to talk with all of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.80,1:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,about what's good here, what's good there, this line,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.16,1:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that scene, this artwork... it was truly a happy thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.20,1:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.59,1:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years did we do this for?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.51,1:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Around three years?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.80,1:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or two?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.68,1:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years? Four or five?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.80,1:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really that long?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.07,1:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're talking about the AfterTalk series specifically,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.64,1:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been doing it for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.16,1:03:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.32,1:04:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's certainly sad that we won't have these opportunities to look back every time,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.03,1:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure there will be other ways
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.47,1:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to interact with everyone, and those opportunities will increase.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.28,1:04:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, if you call on me anytime, as much as you want,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.72,1:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk if there's a place to discuss things like this. And well,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.88,1:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk not just about Haruka's banner, but about Momojan as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.28,1:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even if it doesn't happen every time, maybe at some point for a summary,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.11,1:04:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope there'll be a chance for us to talk
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.43,1:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,together again. I'm just thinking that to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.47,1:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.28,1:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk about all the 3DMVs, for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.68,1:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.03,1:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not Haruka's banner, I'm always told it's okay to watch all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.95,1:04:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They always say it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.28,1:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.76,1:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please watch the past AfterTalks many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.80,1:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As for today's, I'll watch it on my own and reflect.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.11,1:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about it anytime, so I believe that timing will come someday,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.39,1:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pray for it, and for that time, I'll write down various things
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.16,1:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in my notebook again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.47,1:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the short video content will also be increasing,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.47,1:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're putting effort into it, so please
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.80,1:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,look forward to that as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.64,1:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for the event story, "This Story Carries Hope,"
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.39,1:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if there's anyone who hasn't finished watching it yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.84,1:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,once the next event starts,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.39,1:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to read all of it from the event story section.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.51,1:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think there's anyone who hasn't seen it, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.84,1:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spoiled so much up until now,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.88,1:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but please watch the story first.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.11,1:05:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And please rewatch it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.36,1:05:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.59,1:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's meet again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.80,1:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.32,1:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.59,1:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry for my lack of vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun to have the chance to watch the 3DMV together with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.91,1:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and to get comments in real-time like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.68,1:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.95,1:07:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun to have this time where I could empathize with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.51,1:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.55,1:07:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for my otaku rambling.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.76,1:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure there were many parts where you couldn't understand what I was saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.03,1:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.11,1:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's so cool, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.55,1:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is, Haruka is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.72,1:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably become even more
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.80,1:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,unbelievably cool from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.20,1:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her to be like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.91,1:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As a producer, at this timing, you know, like...
